QuestData.Title: ...Why Me?
QuestData.Description:
<The dense, chunky liquid inside the vessel emits a horrendous odor.
The initials O.K. are etched into the side. It seems someone stole Overseer Kalvaros' canteen.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Reclaimed Vessel to Overseer Kalvaros at the Challenger's Promenade.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Deliver the Reclaimed Vessel to Overseer Kalvaros.
QuestData.RewardText:
I've been wondering where my canteen went. Where did you find this, $n? Did you take a drink before returning here?
No matter, I suppose.
